name: Ambulance Family First Aid Kit - Cute Medicine Lock Storage Box
description:
WHAT'S SPECIAL ABOUT THIS MEDICAL STORAGE BOX

Why not keep & organise all your pills and health supplements in a cute ambulance? Designed to alleviate the possible pain with fun, this cute first aid kit features an ambulance and offers a generous capacity with partitions & drawers for easy storage & organisation of all your pills and supplements.Â 

The medicine storage box is also designed for different usage scenarios. The transparent cabinet allows you to conveniently display the most frequently used medicine, while the red light on the top is actually a portable pillbox which could easily fit into your pocket & bag and allow you to accommodate your supplements on the go.
